                        use(href='#goto-detail')
            .preview-box.story-item.careers-post
                img(src='assets/images/c2.png' alt='')
                .title Backend Java Engineer
                .detail As a Backend Java Engineer, your responsibilities include, but are not limited to: • Develop, build, and maintain efficient server-side components•
                a.nav-detail(href='career-detail.html?q=1')
                    | Read Post
                    svg
                        use(href='#goto-detail')
            .preview-box.story-item.careers-post
                img(src='assets/images/c3.png' alt='')
                .title Front-end developer
                .detail As a front-end developer, your tasks include: • Develop, test, and maintain responsive web apps with an elegant UX that delights users and increases productivity.•
                a.nav-detail(href='career-detail.html?q=2')
                    | Read Post
                    svg
                        use(href='#goto-detail')
            .preview-box.story-item.careers-post
                img(src='assets/images/c4.png' alt='')
                .title Senior Data Analyst
                .detail Job Description • Use automated tools to extract data from various sources• Perform analysis to assess data quality and its importance•
                a.nav-detail(href='career-detail.html?q=3')
                    | Read Post
                    svg
                        use(href='#goto-detail')
           
